Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and its application in querying databases. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is also a likely category as the paper discusses the use of natural language to retrieve information from databases. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper discusses the use of machine learning and other AI techniques in natural language to database querying. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper deals with retrieving information from databases using natural language. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the use of machine learning techniques in natural language to database querying.
